author: admin
title: NetApp and RBC to Host a Tech Talk on NetApp's Products and Technology
text:
Submitted by admin on 9/18/2015 @ 1:01 PM   NetApp, Inc. 
SUNNYVALE, CA -- (Marketwired) -- 09/18/15 -- NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP) and RBC will hold a tech talk to discuss NetApp's products and technology with Joel Reich, executive vice president, product operations. Following brief opening remarks from NetApp, a question and answer session will be moderated by RBC. Interested parties can find more information on NetApp's Investor Relations website at http://investors.netapp.com . 
No new financial information will be discussed during this conference call. 
Date: Tuesday, September 22, 2015 Time: 10:00 a.m. Pacific Time / 1:00 p.m. Eastern Time Speaker: Joel Reich, Executive Vice President, Product Operations Moderator: Amit Daryanani, RBC
